  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nStar Atlas: Local Market Gameplay and Infrastructure Contracts\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about updates to Star Atlas SAGE.\nSTAR ATLAS #261 Local Markets ARE HERE. Sell Me Titanium For Mamba!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video about the new local markets.\nWeekly Star Atlas Newsletter #160\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nTown Hall – State of Star Atlas\nStar Atlas TV posted a recording of the latest Star Atlas Town Hall.\nSTAR ATLAS #262 TOWN HALL RECAP DECEMBER 2024 [FREE AIRDROP]\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video summarizing the Town Hall.\nTown Hall Report – December 18, 2024\nAephia published a report on the Town Hall.\nStar Atlas – CommandDeck : News, Releases & More with Njord (SuperPhoenixDAO)!\nNebularTV posted a video of their latest CommandDeck podcast.\nStar Atlas Economic Report 2024 Q4\nStar Atlas published their economic report for the 4th quarter.",
